T02TD2486E:191a-27: nyams pa dag ste bskong bar 'gyur //
T02TD2486E:191a-28: sbyin sreg bzlas brjod gtor ma las //
T02TD2486E:191a-29: byung ba'i dngos grub gsum gyis ni //
T02TD2486E:191a-30: dam tshig nyams pa bskong bar 'gyur //
T02TD2486E:191a-31: thun mong dngos grub grub nas kyang //
T02TD2486E:191a-32: brgyud pas mchog kyang 'grub par gsungs //
T02TD2486E:191a-33: bsgom pa las byung dngos grub kyis //
T02TD2486E:191a-34: dam tshig nyams pa bskongs gyur nas //
T02TD2486E:191a-35: dngos grub gnyis ka thob par 'gyur //
T02TD2486E:191a-36: lhag ma rnams kyi cho ga ni //
T02TD2486E:191a-37: slob dpon rab gsum phar bor nas//
T02TD2486E:191a-38: 'bring gi gsum gyi rab tu bstan //
T02TD2486E:191a-39: tha ma gsum gyi 'bring du bstan //
T02TD2486E:191a-40: tha ma rab kyi sbyin sreg gcig /'bring gi gtor ma'am bzlas brjod bya //
T02TD2486E:191a-41: tha mas bla ma'i mchod pa bya //
T02TD2486E:191a-42: bla ma mchod pa'i man ngag kyang //
T02TD2486E:191a-43: mandala gsum mam gcig byas la //
T02TD2486E:191a-44: mandala mthar phyin mdzes pa la //
T02TD2486E:191a-45: me tog mdzes ldan mchod pa bsags //
T02TD2486E:191a-46: lus tshags bgos pas pus btsugs nas //
T02TD2486E:191a-47: bdun dang bcu dang bcu gnyis dang //
T02TD2486E:191a-48: bya ba cho ga gzhan dang mthun //
T02TD2486E:191a-49: khyad par bdag gi sdig pa ni //
T02TD2486E:191a-50: 'od zer dra bas bsdus nas ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-0: phyung nas gdan gyi pad stengs @191b su //
T02TD2486E:191b-1: bla ma yi dom dkon mchog dang //
T02TD2486E:191b-3: sdig pa sbyong zhing bshags par bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-4: yang na sgyu ma lta bu'i sems //
T02TD2486E:191b-5: de bzhin byas pas dag par 'gyur //
T02TD2486E:191b-6: yan lag cho ga bstan pa ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-7: rtsa ba'i tha ma gsum po dang //
T02TD2486E:191b-8: go rims bzhin du shes par bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-9: khyad par cho ga bstan pa ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-10: rdo rje spun ni bkug gyur nas //
T02TD2486E:191b-11: sgrib spyang lha ru bskyed pa la //
T02TD2486E:191b-12: mchod pa la sogs gong bzhin no //
T02TD2486E:191b-13: de bzhin 'gyur na'ang gong bzhin no //
T02TD2486E:191b-14: bde gshegs bka' 'das dus su ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-15: gang du nyams pa de la ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-16: spyang ba la sogs bya ba dang //
T02TD2486E:191b-17: rigs kyi lha'am phyag mtshan nam //
T02TD2486E:191b-18: a'a li k'a li'i phreng ba ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-19: bstims nas gong bzhin shes par bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-20: sems can byams sems dam tshig la //
T02TD2486E:191b-21: gang du spangs pa de bkug nas //
T02TD2486E:191b-22: dngos dang bsam pa gnyis kas su //
T02TD2486E:191b-23: spyang ba la sogs gong bzhin bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-24: byang sems spong ba de la yang //
T02TD2486E:191b-25: phyi nang yang ni gnyis su bstan //
T02TD2486E:191b-26: phyi ni gong bzhin nang gi ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-27: 'bab ra ka tar ma zin pa'o //
T02TD2486E:191b-28: de yi spyang ba la sogs kun //
T02TD2486E:191b-29: snying ga gong 'og la bstims nas //
T02TD2486E:191b-30: rang gi po ti kho na la //
T02TD2486E:191b-31: gzhan gyi po ti'am dngos de nyid //
T02TD2486E:191b-32: bsam dang dngos la sogs pa ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-33: gong ma bzhin du shes par bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-34: de 'og slar yang smin par bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-35: yang na yi dam lha sogs la //
T02TD2486E:191b-36: gong bzhin khyad par ngag gis spyang //
T02TD2486E:191b-37: phung po lha ru bsams nas ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-38: nang mchod nang gi sbyin sreg ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-39: bsam ste spyang ba'i cho ga bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-40: rang bzhin chos kyi gnas de ru //
T02TD2486E:191b-41: the tshom za ba'i de nyid la //
T02TD2486E:191b-42: rang bzhin de nyid bsams nas su //
T02TD2486E:191b-44: yig 'bru gtum mo la sogs la //
T02TD2486E:191b-45: gtsang mchod la sogs gong bzhin bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-46: sems can gdug pa spyang ba dang //
T02TD2486E:191b-47: bla ma spun la mchod pa bya //
T02TD2486E:191b-48: stong pa'i don la mos pa dang //
T02TD2486E:191b-49: bla ma yi dam dbu steng du //
T02TD2486E:191b-50: chos sku'i rtags dang gtsug tor la //
T02TD2486E:191b-51: khyad par mchod par bya ba'o //
T02TD2486E:191b-52: sems can dad ldan bkug nas ni //
T02TD2486E:191b-53: spyang ba la sogs byas nas kyang //
T02TD2486E:191b-54: dkyil 'khor bsgrub cing dbang bskur dang //
T02TD2486E:192a-2: lhar dmigs mchod pa la sogs bya //
T02TD2486E:192a-3: dam tshig thams cad dran nas kyang //
T02TD2486E:192a-4: thams cad lhar dmigs khyad par ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-5: sad par bya ba la sogs la //
T02TD2486E:192a-6: rigs lnga yab yum bsams nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-7: mchod cing spyang bar bya ba yin //
T02TD2486E:192a-8: shes rab thams cad bkug nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-9: spyang bar byas la lha mor dmigs //
T02TD2486E:192a-10: mchod pa sna tshogs khyad par bsam //
T02TD2486E:192a-11: bdag po dang bcas bkug pa la //
T02TD2486E:192a-12: spyang ba la sogs gong bzhin bya //
T02TD2486E:192a-13: yang na tha mal zhen pa bzlog / mkha' la sogs pa byin brlabs la //
T02TD2486E:192a-14: lha yi rnal 'byor bltas nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-15: phan tshun mchod pas tshim par bya //
T02TD2486E:192a-16: tha mal lce ni sbyangs nas su //
T02TD2486E:192a-17: rdo rje lce ru byin brlabs la //
T02TD2486E:192a-18: gang bshad legs bab gnas pa ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-19: spyang dang lhag bsam la sogs bya //
T02TD2486E:192a-20: khyad par rdo rje 'od zer las //
T02TD2486E:192a-21: bzlas shing mchod pas tshim par bya //
T02TD2486E:192a-22: bstan bya nyid kyang bkug nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-23: gso zhing spyang ba'i cho ga bya //
T02TD2486E:192a-24: rnal 'byor spun rnams bkug nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-25: spyang ba la sogs gong bzhin no //
T02TD2486E:192a-26: snod ldan sems can bkug nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-27: spyang ba la sogs bya ba dang //
T02TD2486E:192a-28: gsang ba dngos dang bsam pa yis //
T02TD2486E:192a-29: bstan la sogs pa bya ba'o //
T02TD2486E:192a-30: dad ldan kun la gong bzhin no//
T02TD2486E:192a-31: spyang ba la sogs dngos dang bsam //
T02TD2486E:192a-32: gnyis ka'i thabs kyis bstan pa yin //
T02TD2486E:192a-33: nyan thos la sogs spyang ba dang //
T02TD2486E:192a-34: bdag nyid spyang bar bya ba'o //
T02TD2486E:192a-35: rnal 'byor lha la nan tan bya'o //
T02TD2486E:192a-36: nga rgyal la sogs spyang ba'o //
T02TD2486E:192a-37: de ltar cho ga byas nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-38: dam tshig nyams pa bskongs nas kyang //
T02TD2486E:192a-39: dngos grub rnam gnyis thob par gsungs //
T02TD2486E:192a-40: las dang po yi gang zag la //
T02TD2486E:192a-41: rtog pa sna tshogs dgur gyur pas //
T02TD2486E:192a-42: rig 'dzin sa ni ma thob par //
T02TD2486E:192a-44: bskang ba'i cho ga ma byas na //
T02TD2486E:192a-45: ngan song gsum dang rdo rje yi //
T02TD2486E:192a-46: dmyal ba dag tu ltung bar 'gyur //
T02TD2486E:192a-47: bskal pa grangs med gnas nas ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-48: de nas bskal par tsha grang myong //
T02TD2486E:192a-49: de nas byol song yi dags su //
T02TD2486E:192a-50: yun ring gnas nas brgya lam na //
T02TD2486E:192a-51: sems can glen lkugs la sogs su //
T02TD2486E:192a-52: yun ring gnas nas tha mar ni //
T02TD2486E:192a-53: sngon gyi dge ba'i sa bon gyis//
T02TD2486E:192b-0: @192b bde gshegs thugs rjes phrad pa dang //
T02TD2486E:192b-1: de ru dam tshig nyams gyur na //
T02TD2486E:192b-2: slar yang thur la ltung bar 'gyur //
T02TD2486E:192b-4: de bas nan tan cher bskyed cing //
T02TD2486E:192b-5: dam tshig sa ya 'bum sde ni //
T02TD2486E:192b-6: lung rgyud kun la'ang gsal bas na //
T02TD2486E:192b-7: shes rab can gyis blang bar bya'o //
T02TD2486E:192b-8: 'di ni blo dman don du gsungs //
T02TD2486E:192b-9: theg pa chen po smod pa dang //
T02TD2486E:192b-10: khyad par gsang sngags smod pa ni //
T02TD2486E:192b-11: bskal pa mtha' yi bar du yang //
T02TD2486E:192b-12: lce la phur bus 'debs shing khro chu ldud //
T02TD2486E:192b-13: de bas gsang sngags 'di la smad par mi bya'o //
T02TD2486E:192b-14: rgyud rnams kun dang mi 'gal tsam du ni //
T02TD2486E:192b-15: dper na sa gzhi lta bu'i dam tshig ni //
T02TD2486E:192b-16: sgrub dang slob dpon rnams la bsten pas su //
T02TD2486E:192b-17: myu gu lta bu'i sangs rgyas 'grub par shog / rin chen phug gi yang steng du //
T02TD2486E:192b-18: snying pos dam tshig nyams pa la //
T02TD2486E:192b-19: bskang ba'i cho ga mi shes pas //
T02TD2486E:192b-20: mkha' 'gro ma yi nad kyis btab //
T02TD2486E:192b-21: de la slob dpon chen pos su //
T02TD2486E:192b-22: rdo rje bstod glus bshags pa yis //
T02TD2486E:192b-23: mkha' 'gro ma la bshags nas kyang //
T02TD2486E:192b-24: mkha' 'gro ma yi rgyud kun du //
T02TD2486E:192b-25: cho ga zab mo sbas pa la //
T02TD2486E:192b-26: yang nas yang du gsol btab pas //
T02TD2486E:192b-27: mkha' 'gro ma yis chos bstan te //
T02TD2486E:192b-28: de ni slob dpon chen po yis //
T02TD2486E:192b-29: bdag gi rna bar brgyud pa 'di //
T02TD2486E:192b-30: phyi nas rnal 'byor don ched du //
T02TD2486E:192b-31: bdag gis rim par bkod pa yang //
T02TD2486E:192b-32: bde gshegs mkha' 'gros bzod par bzhes //
T02TD2486E:192b-33: slob dpon chen po snying po zhabs kyis mdzad pa slob dpon bha bi pa'i gdams ngag mngon par bkod pa rdzogs so//
